	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.QiCanSolve.15": "미스터 치는 당신의 손을 잡는다.",
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.QiCanSolve.16": "이만 가지. 우린 여기서 별로 환영받지 못하나 봐.$a",
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.QiCanSolve.17": "가기 전에 하나 충고해 주지, 캡틴.#$b#지금까지의 약탈로 얻은 것에 만족하도록 해. 네가 겪고 있다는 \\\"불운의 연속\\\"은 막대한 부를 향한 네 더러운 욕망에 지나지 않아.$a#$b#네 욕심이 방금 어떤 결과를 가져올 뻔했는지 잘 봤겠지. 그걸 잘 다스리도록 해. 그렇지 않으면 네 욕망이 널 죽여버릴 테니까.$9",
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.QiCanSolve.18": "캡틴 블랙굴: 무슨 의도로 하는 말이냐?",
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.QiCanSolve.19": "원하는 대로 해석해, 캡틴. 건강해.$8",
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.QiCanSolve.20": "이런 일에 끌어들여서 미안해... 정말 안 다쳤지?$s#$b#진짜 멀쩡해? 천만다행이군.$h",
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.QiCanSolve.21": "캡틴에게 뭘 한 거냐고? 내가 네 머릿속에 들어갔을 때 기억해? 그걸 한 거야, 훨씬 더 거친 방법으로.#$b#내가 초물리적 형태로 누군가의 머리에 침입할 때, 상대방은 식물 인간과 같은 상태가 돼.#$b#그가 질식할 뻔했던 것도 폐가 멈춘 탓이야.#$b#그래서 그날 너에게 그런 꼴로 오래 이야기하지 못한 거야. 널 위험에 빠뜨리고 싶진 않았거든.",
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.QiCanSolve.22": "선글라스 안 낀 모습은 처음 봐...",
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.QiCanSolve.23": "네 눈... 너무 예쁘다.",
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.QiCanSolve.24": "그래, 선글라스 없는 맨 얼굴은 처음이지.$7#$b#사실, 몇 년간 아무에게도 맨 얼굴은 안 보여줬는데...",
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.QiCanSolve.25": "네 눈 정말 예쁘다, 미스터 치...",
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.QiCanSolve.26": "어, 그래, 고마워...$l#$b#사실 맨 눈 드러내는 거 별로 안 좋아해서...$7",
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.QiCanSolve.27": "정말? 고마워, 난 보통 눈을 드러내놓고 다니지 않거든.$l#$b#모나도 내 눈이 참 예쁘다고 말해줬었지... 집에서는 선글라스 벗고 살기를 원하더라.$h#$b#모나는 내 눈을 알고 있는 유일한 사람이었어.$h",
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.QiCanSolve.28": "미스터 치가 선글라스를 쓴다.",
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.QiCanSolve.29": "왜 눈을 가리고 다니냐고? 눈은 사람의 마음이 가장 진솔하게 드러나는 부위야, 눈빛만 봐도 그 사람의 기분을 알 수 있지.#$b#그래서 난 내 눈을 숨기기 위해 선글라스를 쓰는 거야. 약점을 드러내지 않으려고. 이것은 선대 미스터 치에게 배운 거기도 해.#$b#그리고 가벼운 눈맞춤인데도 불구하고 사람들의 마음을 침범하게 되어서... 그런 일을 방지하기 위해 쓰기도 하지.$s",
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.QiCanSolve.30": "캡틴이 날 위협했을 때 걱정해줘서 고마워.$h",
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.QiCanSolve.31": "이제 집에 가야겠다, @. 워프 토템을 쓸게.#$b#유감스럽게도 다른 워프 토템은 가지고 있지 않아서, 네가 집까지 가려면 시간 좀 걸리겠다...",
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.QiCanSolve.32": "@... 혹시 내가... 여기...$s",
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.QiCanSolve.33": "...너랑 여기에 같이 있어주면 좋겠어?",
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.QiCanSolve.34": "응, 나랑 같이 있어줘.",
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.QiCanSolve.35": "아니, 필요 없어. 그냥 집에 가봐, 난 괜찮아.",
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.QiCanSolve.36": "그래 그럼, 내일 보자, @.",
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.QiCanSolve.37": "미스터 치가 워프 토템을 들어 올린다.",
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.QiCanSolve.38": "@, 해적들 틈에서 네가 한 행동이 자꾸 생각나. 네게 그럴 의무는 없었지만, 그래도 날 지켜주려 한 거잖아...#$b#그러니 이건 꼭 알아줬으면 해, 나에게 있어 아주 의미가 큰 행동이었어.$h",

	//Mister Qi stay on the island
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.StayOnIsland.01": "알겠어, 너와 함께 섬에 있을게.$h",
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.StayOnIsland.02": "이제, 우리가 어디서 밤을 보내야 할지 생각해 봐야겠다...",
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.StayOnIsland.03": "미스터 치와 섬의 농가에서 밤을 보냈다.#미스터 치가 잘 잤길 바란다, 그는 정말 불편한 곳에서 잤다...",

	//An Invitation (Part 1) (Mister Qi's 10 hearts event if romance route is unlocked)
	"Event-12.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitation.01": "Hello, @. Surprised to see me?#$b#I was thinking about inviting you to something tonight. We should spend more time together.",//TODO
	"Event-12.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitation.02": "Well, I wanted to invite you to spend the night at my place.$h#$b#I'd like you to sleep with me tonight... What do you think?",//TODO
	"Event-12.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitation.03": "So, you're in? Great! Then come to my house after 8 PM.$h#$b#Remember to finish your daily tasks before you go, okay? We'll spend the whole night together.",//TODO

	//An Invitation (Part 2) (Mister Qi's 10 hearts event if romance route is unlocked)
	"Event-13.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2.01": "Hi, @. I was waiting for you! Come on in.$h",//TODO
	"Event-13.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2.02": "Well, now we're here together. What do you want to do first, @?",//TODO
	"Event-13.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2.03": "Do you want to see my eyes again? Yeah, it's been a while since you've seen them. You didn't even pay much attention to them the first time.#$b#All right, I'll take off my glasses, and then we can do whatever you want.$h",//TODO
	"Event-13.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2.04": "Your eyes are so beautiful, Mr. Qi... I can't help but admire them.",//TODO
	"Event-13.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2.05": "You should let people see your eyes, Mr. Qi.",//TODO
	"Event-13.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2.06": "Haha, it's funny that the only two people who've seen my eyes had the same reaction.$h#$b#I wonder what makes them so special to you, after all?$l",//TODO
	"Event-13.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2.07": "It's just that I don't know if it will be a good idea... Only you and Mona have seen my eyes, and you were both amazed by them. Imagine how other people would react.$s#$b#It would draw too much attention, and that's not good for us as Misters Qi. We should always be discreet. The blue skin's already enough of a spotlight...$u",//TODO
	"Event-13.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2.08": "However, I can make an exception if you want...$l",//TODO
	"Event-13.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2.09": "Look at the time, @! It's almost bedtime, and we haven't done anything yet...#$b#How about we prepare something to eat together? You must be hungry. What do you think?",//TODO
	"Event-13.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2.10": "Great, then let's go to the kitchen and prepare something!$h",//TODO
	"Event-13.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2.11": "What do you want to eat, @? We can prepare any dish you like!",//TODO
	"Event-13.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2.12": "Seriously, any dish at all. Just pick something, and we'll roll up our sleeves and get cooking!",//TODO
	"Event-13.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2.13": "So, what do you want to eat?",//TODO
	"Event-13.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2.14": "How about spaghetti?",//TODO
	"Event-13.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2.15": "What do you think of pizza, Mr. Qi?",//TODO
	"Event-13.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2.16": "I'm in the mood for something related to the sea but also spicy... How about Spicy Eel?",//TODO
	"Event-13.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2.17": "Actually, I'm not sure what to eat... What's your favorite dish, Mr. Qi?",//TODO

	//Spaghetti
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.CookingSpaghettiWithQi.01": "Spaghetti, huh? Alright then. It's a good choice and a dinner classic, too.#$b#I'll get the things we'll need.",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.CookingSpaghettiWithQi.02": "Okay, everything we need to make spaghetti is here.#$b#Now comes the fun part: cooking!$h",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.CookingSpaghettiWithQi.03": "Mr. Qi and I made spaghetti together. It was so much fun!",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.CookingSpaghettiWithQi.04": "Thank you so much for agreeing to spend tonight with me, @. Making this dish with you was really fun.$h#$b#I enjoy spending time with you. We should do things like this more often.$l",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.CookingSpaghettiWithQi.05": "Anyway, let's eat. Pasta cools down fast, so it's better to eat it while it's still hot!",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.CookingSpaghettiWithQi.06": "The spaghetti was delicious, wasn't it, Mr. Qi?",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.CookingSpaghettiWithQi.07": "Yes, it really was! Truly delicious, actually.$h#$b#Maybe you've made spaghetti my new favorite dish?$l",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.CookingSpaghettiWithQi.08": "... Forget what I said... Let's keep going. I want to do a few more things before bed.$7",//TODO

	//Pizza
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.CookingPizzaWithQi.01": "Pizza's a great choice, @! It goes really well with relaxed moments like this.$h#$b#I'll get everything we need to make one.",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.CookingPizzaWithQi.02": "Well, we've got everything to make our pizza, @. Let's get our hands dirty, literally!$h",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.CookingPizzaWithQi.03": "Mr. Qi and I made the pizza together. It was so much fun! Now we just have to wait for it to finish baking!",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.CookingPizzaWithQi.04": "It's ready, @! I'll get it.$h",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.CookingPizzaWithQi.05": "Looks delicious, doesn't it, @?",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.CookingPizzaWithQi.06": "So, what are we waiting for? Let's slice it!$h",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.CookingPizzaWithQi.07": "The first slice is for you, @.#$b#The second is mine!$h",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.CookingPizzaWithQi.08": "Hmm, it's really good! And I don't even like pizza that much!$h#$b#Preparing food with our own hands gives it a different flavor, doesn't it, @?",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.CookingPizzaWithQi.09": "Anyway, let's finish eating and do something else. I want to enjoy our night a little more before bed...$h",//TODO

	//Spicy Eel
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.CookingSpicyEelWithQi.01": "Spicy Eel is a good call! Let's do it!$h",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.CookingSpicyEelWithQi.02": "Alright, we have everything we need to make Spicy Eel! Let's get started.$h",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.CookingSpicyEelWithQi.03": "We both started preparing the dish.",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.CookingSpicyEelWithQi.04": "Okay, @. We're almost done; we just need to put it in the oven. I'll turn it on, and then you put the dish inside, okay?",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.CookingSpicyEelWithQi.05": "Mr. Qi went easy on the pepper in this dish. Should I add more?",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.CookingSpicyEelWithQi.06": "Add more pepper.",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.CookingSpicyEelWithQi.07": "Keep it as it is.",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.CookingSpicyEelWithQi.08": "I added more pepper to the dish without Mr. Qi knowing. I hope it wasn't too much...",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.CookingSpicyEelWithQi.09": "I left the dish as it is. What if I overdid the pepper?",//TODO

	//Add more pepper to the dish
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.iWantMoreSpicy.01": "@, you added more pepper to this food, didn't you?",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.iWantMoreSpicy.02": "What?! Of course not, Mr. Qi!",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.iWantMoreSpicy.03": "No use lying to me, @. I know you added more pepper here.#$b#Did you forget I can see everything that happens in the world?$8",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.iWantMoreSpicy.04": "Mr. Qi takes a bottle of milk from the fridge and puts it on the table.",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.iWantMoreSpicy.05": "Well, I hope you can handle pepper, because I've already put in plenty.$8#$b#Enjoy your meal, if you can handle it.$9",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.iWantMoreSpicy.06": "It's too spicy!",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.iWantMoreSpicy.07": "I told you. There was plenty already, but you went ahead and added even more.$a",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.iWantMoreSpicy.08": "Mr. Qi keeps eating like it's nothing.",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.iWantMoreSpicy.09": "Hey, give me that bottle!",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.iWantMoreSpicy.10": "Oh, you wanted the milk? Too bad... It's all gone.$9",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.iWantMoreSpicy.11": "You're so mean, Mr. Qi!",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.iWantMoreSpicy.12": "And you're too weak for pepper! Haha!$h#$b#There's more milk in the fridge, @. Just grab it.",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.iWantMoreSpicy.13": "And now, how are we supposed to eat a dish this spicy?",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.iWantMoreSpicy.14": "We can use Qi Seasoning. It should take away the extra heat.",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.iWantMoreSpicy.15": "Mr. Qi used the seasoning he made on our dishes; now, it's absolutely delicious! Spicy in just the right amount!",//TODO

	//Kept it at it is
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.NormalDish.01": "Looks pretty good, huh, @? I think we make a great team in the kitchen.$h",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.NormalDish.02": "Anyway, enjoy your meal!$h",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.NormalDish.03": "Hey, I'm not usually a big fan of spicy food, but this dish is really good, isn't it?#$b#It seems that making something together with you makes everything completely different—in a good way.$l",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.NormalDish.04": "Anyway, let's finish eating. I want to enjoy more of this night with you.$l",//TODO

	//Qi's Favorite Dish
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.QisFavoriteDish.01": "Hmm... My favorite dish is Fried Mushroom. What do you think about making that for dinner?",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.QisFavoriteDish.02": "Okay, so let's make Fried Mushroom for dinner! Let's get the things to prepare.#$b#You get the utensils and I'll get the ingredients, okay?",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.QisFavoriteDish.03": "Ah, I've always liked Fried Mushroom, but it only became my favorite dish because of the way Mona made it, you know...$l#$b#She had a different way of preparing it. It was so tasty when she made it... I've tried making it her way, but it never tastes the same.$6",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.QisFavoriteDish.04": "No, @, it's okay. I still want to make this dish, I think it'll be fun. Let's go ahead.",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.QisFavoriteDish.05": "Mr. Qi and I prepared the dish together. It was so much fun!",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.QisFavoriteDish.06": "Thank you so much for agreeing to spend this night with me, @. I really enjoy doing things with you.$h#$b#We should do this more often, but I understand that you're very busy and sometimes you might not have time for these things. Sometimes, I don't either.$l",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.QisFavoriteDish.07": "Anyway, let's eat before our food gets cold! Enjoy your meal, @.$h",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.QisFavoriteDish.08": "Mr. Qi suddenly stops eating. He looks emotional.",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.QisFavoriteDish.09": "@... The taste of this dish... It's just like the one Mona used to make...$6#$b#Actually... It's even better! It's delicious.$h",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.QisFavoriteDish.10": "I have no idea how we managed to do this... We didn't use Qi Seasoning and followed the recipe exactly. How could the flavor turn out so good?",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.QisFavoriteDish.11": "I think that all this time, the different flavor I tasted in this dish was, in fact... a manifestation of love...$l",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.QisFavoriteDish.12": "Yeah, I think that's it... Making this dish together really added a different flavor.$l#$b#It's such a unique flavor... I don't think even if I used Qi Seasoning I'd get this result.$h",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.QisFavoriteDish.13": "Maybe love is a seasoning that can't be replicated.",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.QisFavoriteDish.14": "You always try to find logical explanations to understand what you feel. I think that's cute!",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.QisFavoriteDish.15": "Yeah, maybe you're right. It seems that love is so unique it's even above the Misters Qi.$h#$b#And honestly, I'm so happy to be able to experience it again with you...$l",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.QisFavoriteDish.16": "Haha... Well... I think this insistence on finding logic in things that sometimes don't have any is rooted in all Misters Qi...$7#$b#I've been trying to change that and accept that not everything needs an explanation, but it's hard to break a habit so deeply ingrained in us.$s",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.QisFavoriteDish.17": "Anyway, let's finish eating. I want to do other things before we go to bed.",//TODO

	//Continue the event
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.01": "I usually do a few different things before bed during the week so my routine doesn't get too repetitive, you know?#$b#Today, I was planning to finish a book I started last week. There are several books you can read here, too. You can read one if you like.",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.02": "Oh, no! I need to do something in the lab. I have to check {{AlienName}}'s vital signs.#$b#Sorry, @, but I need to go there; it's urgent...",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.03": "No, you don't need to come with me; it won't take long. I'll be right back, okay? You can grab any book to read.",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.04": "Mr. Qi enters the lab.",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.05": "It looks like this book is Mona's diary.",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.06": "You open a random page of her diary.",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.07": "\\\"Summer 8: Today, Sandy told me Emily had prepared a surprise for Gus tonight to celebrate his birthday. The whole village could join. Sandy asked if I was going, and I said yes. After all, if everyone was going, why couldn't I?\\\"#\\\"And, of course, I went with Azure. It had been a while since we'd gone out, so I decided to combine business with pleasure. But I think it wasn't a good idea.\\\"",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.08": "?#Why wasn't it a good idea?",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.09": "You continue reading.",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.10": "... Happy birthday to you!",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.11": "Aw, guys, you didn't have to do this...$s",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.12": "And you really thought we'd let your birthday go unnoticed, Gus? No way!$h#$b#You're too special to us! Right, guys?$h",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.13": "YEEES!",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.14": "Ah, guys, come on... You're gonna make me emotional...$s#$b#Wanna know something? Since you did all this for me, I'll return the favor, too!",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.15": "Free drinks for everyone tonight!$h",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.16": "WOOHOO!",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.17": "\\\"... After Gus announced free drinks for everyone, Azure and I stepped away from the crowd. He didn't want to be around so many people.\\\"",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.18": "It's much quieter here, away from that crowd and noise.",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.19": "C'mon, Azure, it's not that many people, right?$h#$b#But I agree—they are pretty noisy!",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.20": "By the way, have you decided what you're going to drink, Mona?",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.21": "Honestly, I'm not planning to drink anything tonight. I need to keep working on my thesis tomorrow morning, so I don't want a hangover.$s#$b#Maybe I'll have a soda; I don't know... But what about you? Are you thinking of drinking?",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.22": "Yeah, I was thinking about getting something to drink—just to taste it again, you know?#$b#It's been so long since I drank that I've forgotten the taste. It's been almost twelve years since I last drank alcohol.",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.23": "Wow, twelve years? That's a long time! I hope you're not planning to make up for those twelve dry years tonight! Hahaha!$h",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.24": "Hahaha, very funny... I know how to control myself. You won't be leaving here with a drunk.$u",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.25": "Okay, if you say so, then it's settled, Mr. Self-Control.$h",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.26": "Want me to get you something?",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.27": "Spaghetti, please!",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.28": "\\\"Telling him not to overdo it with the drinks was completely pointless; it went in one ear and out the other. He started feeling sick after a few drinks. For someone who hadn't drunk in so long, it was much more than I expected.\\\"",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.29": "Azure, are you okay? Don't you think you've had enough?",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.30": "I didn't drink too much... just four drinks...$s",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.31": "Four drinks is already a lot, Azure. It's been over ten years since you last drank, remember?#$b#Do you want to go home? We can leave. I just wanted to stop by here.",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.32": "Yeah, maybe I overdid it a little... Can we go home? I'm getting sleepy...$h",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.33": "Of course, let's go home. Come here, hold my hand. I'll help you up.",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.34": "Mona! What happened to Azure? Is he okay?",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.35": "Oh, hi, Sandy. He drank too much, so I'm taking him home to rest.",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.36": "I didn't drink too much... I already said...",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.37": "Got it. Do you need help? I can give you a ride.",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.38": "Of course! Any help is welcome!$h",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.39": "\\\"With Sandy's help, I took Azure back home. It's great having her as a friend.\\\"#\\\"Anyway, taking care of drunk Azure was... different from what I was used to.\\\"",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.40": "C'mon, Azure! Get up! You're better off in bed!$a",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.41": "The bedroom floor's so nice and cool, love. C'mere, stay with me... just a little while, okay? Please...$h",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.42": "Ugh, Azure, seriously?! You need to rest...$a",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.43": "Pretty please?...",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.44": "Okay, okay... I will. No need to beg like that...$7",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.45": "See? Isn't the floor cold? Feels nice, right?$h",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.46": "Yeah, it is pretty cold...",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.47": "\\\"He got all goofy—laughing for no reason, talking softly... It seems like the alcohol brought out a side of him I never imagined he had.\\\"#\\\"Honestly, I couldn't resist when he gave me that puppy-dog look, begging me to lie down on the floor with him... It was so cute!\\\"",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.48": "\\\"After we lay there for a while, he let me take him to bed to sleep.\\\"",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.49": "Good night, Azure.",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.50": "Good night, my love...$l",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.51": "\\\"Before I could leave the room, he called me again.\\\"",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.52": "Mona...$s",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.53": "What is it, Azure?",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.54": "I'm getting hot...",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.55": "*Sigh* Okay, I'll help you. I forgot you sweat a lot at night... Sorry.$s",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.56": "\\\"I thought he wouldn't even feel hot, given how drunk he was, but I was wrong...\\\"#\\\"When I left the room, I found myself laughing. I never imagined I'd see him in such a... vulnerable way. He didn't even seem like the same Azure I met on Ginger Island.\\\"",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.57": "\\\"About fifteen minutes after I left him sleeping, he showed up in the living room in just his underwear—the same way he'd gone to bed. He got up and went straight to the living room.\\\"",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.58": "Azure, what are you doing? I thought you were already asleep. Did something happen?",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.59": "Azure, why aren't you saying anything? Are you sleepwalking?$a",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.60": "\\\"He put on some music, held my hand, lifted me off the sofa, and pulled me close to him. He didn't seem to be sleepwalking; he was looking me in the eyes. I tried asking again...\\\"",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.61": "What are you doing, Azure?$l",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.62": "\\\"When I asked again, he seemed to hear me. Then he said...\\\"",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.63": "Earth to @, Earth to @. Can you hear me?$a",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.64": "Looks like your reading was pretty immersive, huh? You didn't even notice when I came back.#$b#What were you reading, huh?$8",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.65": "Oh, an entry from Mona's diary? I see...#$b#Which entry were you on? Can I see?",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.66": "You give the diary to Mr. Qi.",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.67": "Oh, it's the entry from Gus's birthday...$7",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.68": "Mr. Qi looks visibly embarrassed.",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.69": "She didn't have to write those... things in her diary.$7#$b#She only did it because she knew I wouldn't break my promise not to see her writing the entries with the extra-physical representation...$7#$b#I would never have allowed her to write that stuff... It's embarrassing.$a",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.70": "I don't get it. Why does that embarrass you, Mr. Qi? You were just drunk. From what I read, you were being pretty romantic.",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.71": "That's because you didn't read the whole thing, and thankfully you didn't... I wouldn't have anywhere to hide my face if you'd read everything she wrote here.$7",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.72": "@, I know you want to ask something. What do you want to know? Go ahead.",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.73": "While I was reading, I was imagining the whole scene. You interrupted me at the part where you pulled Mona close after waking up...#She wrote that you said something, but I couldn't read it. What did you say to her?",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.74": "Oh, that part where I went to the living room minutes after she put me to bed?#$b#Well, I said I wanted to dance with her, so we did. Then I fell asleep in her arms. That's what happened.",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.75": "What will I do with this diary? Honestly, I don't know.#$b#I wanted it to be kept so it could be read by future Misters Qi, so they could better know the person who was responsible for changing our entire history.#$b#But at the same time, there are things here I didn't want anyone to read—not even me.$7",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.76": "Why don't you keep this diary just for yourself and no one else? Your word should be enough for the future Misters Qi, right?",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.77": "Why don't you write a book about her importance to the Misters Qi and keep the diary for yourself?",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.78": "Yes, you're right. It's not necessary to leave this diary for future Misters Qi to read. What matters to us about her story is safe with me. I won't forget.$h#$b#But one thing I know: you really want to read the rest of this entry, don't you, @?",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.79": "Well, you can keep wanting. I don't want you reading the rest of this entry.",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.80": "Mr. Qi uses magic and erases the rest of the entry from Summer 8.",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.81": "Hey, that's a great idea, @! I can write down everything important and leave out the irrelevant details.$h#$b#I don't know how I didn't think of that before. Actually, I did, but I didn't think it would be necessary.#$b#Now that I've seen what Mona wrote in this entry, I realize that if I want future Misters Qi to know her story, I'll have to rewrite it myself.#$b#There's a lot of irrelevant stuff for us here.",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.82": "Oh, and I'll erase the rest of this entry, too. I know you read Mona's diary occasionally, and I don't want you reading the rest of this entry.#$b#I'll leave only what you've already read.",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.83": "Wow, it's really late already... I was thinking of doing one more thing before bed, but I don't think we'll have time.$s#$b#The problem {{AlienName}} faced took longer to solve than I expected...$s",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.84": "You know, @... When I invited you to spend the night with me, I wanted to spend more time by your side and do things together.#$b#Making dinner with you was really fun, but then I had to go to my lab to solve a problem...#$b#I could have asked you to come along, but I thought it would be quick, so I didn't even think to ask.$s#$b#In the end, I spent more time away from you than with you. Even after inviting you over, I still managed to find a way to distance myself...$s",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.85": "I know it was important and couldn't wait... but, you know, would it have hurt to ask if you wanted to come with me?#$b#This habit of focusing only on responsibilities sometimes makes me distance myself from the people I love without even realizing it...$s#$b#Sadly, it's a trait all Misters Qi share. After all, we've spent generations living solely to fulfill our mission and nothing else.#$b#I'm the first Mister Qi to have a life parallel to our mission. Breaking a generational habit is hard.$s#$b#I've been trying to change that for us, but sometimes it's tough.$s",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.86": "What I'm trying to say is that even though we haven't done many romantic things together, I cherish the few moments we've shared and every conversation we've had since you decided to help me.$l#$b#And I want you to know that even if I don't always show it through actions, I love you very much, @.$l",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.87": "Now, let's go to sleep. It's very late, and you need to wake up early tomorrow to take care of your farm.$h#$b#You know what, @? Starting today, you don't need to enter here before Sandy's shop closes anymore. You can come in anytime you want.",//TODO
	"Event-Fork.MrQiRealNPC.AnInvitationPart2_Continue.88": "Good night, {{PlayerName}}.",//TODO

